COMMENT ON TABLE OFFENDER_COURSE_ATTENDANCES IS 'Records all schedule dates for offenders arising from placements into programs of any type (accredited programs, community service and institutional activities). Offender program schedule records may be physical (stored in this table) or virtual (derived from a schedule pattern for the course/activity to which the offender has been allocated). For every virtual program-schedule record, the system automatically creates a physical record in this table in an overnight routine the night before the schedule date, to ensure that the physical record exists for recording attendance and for historical attendance.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN OFFENDER_COURSE_ATTENDANCES.EVENT_ID IS 'Unique identifier for this offender schedule record, or NULL for virtual schedules (schedules determined from the underlying schedule pattern).';
COMMENT ON COLUMN OFFENDER_COURSE_ATTENDANCES.CRS_ACTY_ID IS 'Unique identifier associating this attendance record to a particular delivery of a program.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN OFFENDER_COURSE_ATTENDANCES.OFFENDER_BOOK_ID IS 'System generated unique identifier for an offender booking.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN OFFENDER_COURSE_ATTENDANCES.OFFENDER_PRG_OBLIGATION_ID IS 'For accredited programs, unique identifier associating this attendance record with an offender''s program obligation.';
