COMMENT ON COLUMN OFFENDER_COURSE_ATTENDANCES.PROGRAM_ID IS 'Unique identifier of the program / service.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN OFFENDER_COURSE_ATTENDANCES.EVENT_CLASS IS 'Classifies this scheduled event as one of three schedule classes: EXT_MOV (institutional external movements), INT_MOV (institutional internal movements) and COMM (community movements including community service, programs and appointments).';
